title: AIIMS Bhopal Jobs 2026 - Apply Online for 02 Project Technician III, Data Entry Operator Posts
description: The All India Institute of Medical Sciences, Bhopal ( AIIMS Bhopal) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 02 Project Technician III, Data Entry Operator Jobs. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their B.E./B. Tech in Electrical, Mechanical Engineering, 12th can apply for the AIIMS Bhopal Jobs 2026. The interested applicants can apply in online mode. ...
